OL,3,C'Stop being so bored!': Sarah Ferguson
OL,4,Cscolds stars at charity auction
OL,6,FSarah Ferguson appeared to be furious
OL,7,Fat Cannes Film Festival on Wednesday
OL,8,Fnight, as she attempted to silence a
OL,9,Fnoisy crowd.
OL,11,Fwas speaking at a charity event that
OL,12,Fwas part of the festival, where she
OL,13,Fwas helping to auction off a painting
OL,14,Fof the late Queen Elizabeth II.
OL,16,FDemi Moore, Heidi Klum and Kelly
OL,17,FRowland were among the stars in
OL,18,Fattendance. Cher also performed a four-
OL,19,Fsong set at the event.
