OL,3,C'Stop being so bored!': Sarah Ferguson
OL,4,Cscolds stars at charity auction
OL,6,F"The entire room right now needs to be
OL,7,Fquiet," the said, as she thanked
OL,8,Fauctioneer Simon de Pury, who was
OL,9,Ftaking bids for the "exceptional"
OL,10,Fpainting in aid of charity.
OL,12,FShe berated the crowd for "saying 'I
OL,13,Fwant to go, where is the next
OL,14,Fparty?'", and for looking uninterested
OL,15,Fin what she was saying.
OL,17,F"Will all of you stop being so bored,
OL,18,Fstop looking at your wine glass, stop
OL,19,Flooking at your watch, and let's do
OL,20,Fit," she said, eliciting cheers from
OL,21,Fthe crowd.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/4
