OL,3,C'Stop being so bored!': Sarah Ferguson
OL,4,Cscolds stars at charity auction
OL,6,F"But what I want to say," she
OL,7,Fcontinued, "is why are we here? What
OL,8,Fis the future? And why aren't we
OL,9,Fmaking our planet better for the youth
OL,10,Fof tomorrow?"
OL,12,FShe said that she was "so sorry" to
OL,13,Fyoung people today for "completely and
OL,14,Futterly destroying" the planet.
OL,16,FBut she said that thanks to charities
OL,17,Fsuch as amfAR - which the event was in
OL,18,Faid of - and the "scientific
OL,19,Fbrilliance" of the people who work
OL,20,Fthere, a difference could be made.
