OL,6,FamfAR, or The Foundation for AIDS
OL,7,FResearch, is an American non-profit
OL,8,Fdedicated to researching the virus and
OL,9,FHIV prevention.
OL,11,FShe ended her speech with a call to
OL,12,Faction, saying "let's get this going".
OL,14,FThe painting was auctioned off for
OL,15,F475,000 Euros (#405,000), with all
OL,16,Fproceeds donated to amFAR.
